text: King Carl XIV and Queen Silvia, O'Neill's mother Eva Maria Walter, as well as Adrienne's six godparents, Coralie Charriol Paul, Nader Panahpour, Natalie Werner, Anouska d'Abo, Gustav Thott, and Carlotte Kreuger Cederlund, are all included in one of the portraits. Not pictured are the royal couple's two eldest children, Princess Leonore, 4, and Prince Nicolas, 2. Princess Madeleine gave birth to the newborn on March 9 in Stockohlm. Her husband expressed their excitement in a statement, sharing at the time, ` ` We are thrilled about the new addition to our family. Leonore and Nicolas are looking very much forward to finally meeting their new little sister.''
